## The Moat (what makes us hard to copy)
 
Most workplace AI is being layered onto systems people barely use. Workvivo starts somewhere far more powerful: **attention, habit, trust, daily behaviour.** Five moats Microsoft cannot easily replicate:
 
- **Attention.** 9 million employees opening Workvivo by habit. Not licensed reach. Real daily ritual. Microsoft can buy more features. They cannot buy our habit.
- **AI built in, not bolted on.** Zoom AI Companion is our unfair advantage — deep R&D, $1B invested, rapid pace of innovation, federated across model providers. We don't compete on the model layer; we compose it.
- **Cross-pillar signal sharing.** Comms triggers Search triggers Seer. The AI learns what no point tool can see.
- **Frontline reach.** We built the product for the 80% Copilot doesn't license. Mobile-first, offline-capable, real-time translation, no email required. HQ closes the frontline AI gap.
- **Level 3 governance.** Zero data retention with model providers. No training on customer content. EU residency via AWS Bedrock. Most enterprise AI cannot claim all three.
