## The Model (does the math hold)
 
- **Pricing:** $4 platform + $2 HQ AI = **$6 per user per month.** HQ+ at $10. HQ+ Enterprise (the full agentic version, on request only) at $24.
- **Profit margin:** ~50% blended on the bundle. The AI tier alone runs at ~6% — deliberately thin to drive adoption, not a permanent margin position.
- **At enterprise scale (~410K HQ users):** A single contract approaches **$30M a year**, with **$9.8M of that as AI revenue.** Seer Standalone gives us a parallel sales motion that doesn't require a full Workvivo platform deal.
- **Versus the competition on AI alone:** **15x cheaper than Copilot. 22x cheaper than Glean.** Same job — but available to the entire workforce, not just the desk holder.
